  Description

This repository contains my configuration files, documents and scripts
for vim,mutt,zsh and a lot of softwares


    Vim

      Features

        C-support (http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=213)
        Omlet for ocaml (www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1196)
  	FuzzyFinder (https://bitbucket.org/ns9tks/vim-fuzzyfinder/)
	NerdTree (https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree)
	ProtoDef (https://github.com/ewiplayer/vim-protodef)
	OmniCpp (http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1520)
	A.vim (http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=31)

        And a lot of useful or useless things

      Shell environment

        -FULLNAME, Contain your full name; if it is not defined it is equal to
        your username

        -EMAIL, Contain your email; if not defined, equal to username@epita.fr

        -NO_STRICT_EPITA_HEADERS, defined it if you want to use non-strict
        headers

        -EPITA_STRICT, Declared it if you must respect the epita's coding style


PS
	My configuration has been created by me and for me; they has been build
	in order to follow the coding style of my school, it
	probably contain a lot of useless stuff for a casual personn
	(like a coding style checking)


If you have any sugestion, question feel free to contact me at
